   "source": [
    "# Colors"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "This library uses the [Accessible Color Sequences for Data Visualization](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2107.02270) by Matthew A. Petroff."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {
    "editable": true,
    "mystnb": {
     "code_prompt_show": "Show imports"
    },
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": ""
    },
    "tags": [
     "hide-cell"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%load_ext autoreload\n",
    "%autoreload 2\n",
    "\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import xplt\n",
    "\n",
    "xplt.apply_style()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Usage"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "editable": true,
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": ""
    },
    "tags": []
   },
   "source": [
    "With {meth}`xplt.apply_style` in the import section above, the default color cycle is updated to use the petroff colors.  \n",
    "The colors are also accessible by name as `p0`, `p1`, ... `p9` even without applying Xplt's style:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {
    "editable": true,
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": ""
    },
    "tags": []
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 500x100 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(5, 1))\n",
    "plt.plot(np.linspace(5, 0) % 2)\n",
    "plt.plot(np.linspace(0, 5) % 2, color=\"p2\");"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Colormaps can be used like `cmap='petroff_bipolar'`:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {
    "tags": []
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "t = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, 1024)\n",
    "data2d = np.sin(t)[:, np.newaxis] * np.cos(t)[np.newaxis, :]\n",
    "im = ax.imshow(data2d, cmap=\"petroff_bipolar\")\n",
    "fig.colorbar(im, ax=ax, label=\"Color\");"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
